Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OnNVT2uvTMwQ7kNvgF___Dy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD90dw5Ik4LBvSmen2PqrEfm-QNd_MEb9jnyHV9wPzsDA&oe=66FBCE7A"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DPqwlpfscIMQ7kNvgF6fVrI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAMRmdyEfcbd_lPup9Qq3WhE7ta1lNMfUsdSHMdQM5ITQ&oe=66FBEE43"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zHFsAbK4FcUQ7kNvgGf88x_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCSjjMAjol2aZpeCTxcoS9Xd3IhenUhLU2B8N-nCTA9Kg&oe=66FBC433"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jQcx2tX1YVYQ7kNvgEest22&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAUPiao1d9lKd52m0-fvhzjE9e9v2yVSQ_XRGngJye7Dw&oe=66FBECC0"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1151595012723300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982662_1151595016056633_8079137566055371486_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid