fe0f\u20e3 Defend a speech in front of an audience to improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Train your strengths in a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Make decisions to develop your strategic and analytical skills.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Work as part of a team to foster collaboration and group efficiency.", "short_description": "Boost your \"Soft Skills\" with our Virtual Reality Simulator! \n\nComposed of 5 training capsules to: \n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Self-assess your transversal competences.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Speed up decision making.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Promote teamwork.\n\nIdeal for professionals looking to improve their interpersonal skills in an immersive, interactive and effective way!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PW4DHoiC6GYQ7kNvgHvt0H-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAhjWIoN8l_lmyKaZrgAPsXibO-ZYihyQ6AbmUNFNi9eQ&oe=66FBDFE9"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8rlJoeXGKzUQ7kNvgFt7yFb&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5R2g7lN8Ws7GQpW-IbpXWb-n9qtnjWsCmkr0IBrME0g&oe=66FBF8AF"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dLAZFizIKS0Q7kNvgHcUj8D&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAwHGgA0kpMVtkKZwNu08Ko1o9TpiR0-nqBVa9x5qNbkQ&oe=66FBEDF3"}, 